new file mode 100644
index 0000000..061b7d5
--- /dev/null
+++ b/RIGGING.md
@@ -0,0 +1,55 @@
+# Rigging
+
+Project tooling values for Shipshape roles. Values only, not procedure.
+Procedure lives in the skills. Every role reads this on open.
+
+## Stack
+
+- language: JavaScript
+- runtime: node
+- packageManager: npm
+
+## Directories
+
+- implementation: src
+- specs: features
+- verification: features/steps
+- verification: features/support
+- assets: data
+- scantlings: none
+
+## Commands
+
+- discover: `npx cucumber-js --dry-run --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- focused: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright" {scenario}`
+- broad: `npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- coverage: `npx c8 --reporter=text npx cucumber-js --tags "not @captain and not @shipwright"`
+- step-usage: `npx cucumber-js --format usage-json`
+- plank-inventory: `npx jsdoc -X src/`
+- typecheck: none
+- lint: none
+- conformance: none
+
+## Perturbation
+
+- message: `PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed`
+- perturb: `throw new Error("PERTURBATION: consider current durable context; remove when fixed");`
+
+## Tiers
+
+- default: @logic
+- sandbox: none
+- policy: @logic no credentials required
+- weather: logs/weather.json
+- runrecord: logs/runrecord.jsonl
+
+## Dependencies
+
+- policy: locked
+- dependency: @cucumber/cucumber
+
+## Outbound
+
+- outbound: none
+- ship: none
+- verify: none
diff --git a/features/methodology.feature b/features/methodology.feature
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..0d6d364
--- /dev/null
+++ b/features/methodology.feature
@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@
+Feature: Methodology conformance
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Watchbill shape conformance
+    Given project configuration
+    When watchbill.json exists
+    Then the file contains only ordered watch objects named watch1 and onward
+    And each watch contains only a scenarios array of references or tier tags from RIGGING.md
+
+  @captain @conformance
+  Scenario: Perturbation quiescence
+    Given no uncommitted verification run with planted violations
+    When every source file under implementation is searched for the PERTURBATION token
+    Then no source file contains the PERTURBATION token
